-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.10 Verification Steps
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check interface configuration
ip addr show
ip -6 addr show

Check routing table
ip route show
ip -6 route show

Test connectivity to gateway (fw)
From int-srv01:
ping -c 3 10.1.10.1
ping6 -c 3 2001:db8:1001:10::1

From DMZ servers:
ping -c 3 10.1.20.1
ping6 -c 3 2001:db8:1001:20::1

From jamie-ws01:
ping -c 3 1.1.1.10
ping6 -c 3 2001:db8:1111::10

Test cross-network connectivity (after fw routing enabled)
From int-srv01 to DMZ server:
ping -c 3 10.1.20.10

From jamie-ws01 to int-srv01:
ping -c 3 10.1.10.10


